				<div class="help">
				    How much does it cost?  Very little, really.
				</div>
			    </td>
			    <td>Free</td>
			    <td><div>$5 / month</div> or <div>$50 / year</div></td>
			</tr>


			<tr>
			    <td colspan="3">
				<div class="help w100 text-center">
				    * Unlimited means as much as you can, limited
				    only by the items in your backpack.  Obviously.
				</div>
			    </td>
			</tr>
		    </table>
		</div>
